GUI - load file(processing)
	- save as
	- error log
	- preview

Input: text files -> processing -> formatted files

defaults: 80 chars per line
		  left
		  merge lines


-r right justification
-c center
-l left shifted
-t centered, no justification
 
-d double space
-s single space

-i indent on 1st line, 5 spaces
-b indent multiple lines, 10 spaces
-n indent block ends

-2 2 columns, 35chs/10chs/35chs
-1 1 column

-e blank line